export const INTRODUCED_BILLS_URL = 'https://api.propublica.org/congress/v1/115/house/bills/introduced.json';
export const get_SPECIFIC_BILL = (congress, billId) => `https://api.propublica.org/congress/v1/${congress}/bills/${bill - id}.json`
